Package: fix-cloud-init-dns
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Tu Nombre <tu@email.com>
Depends: resolvconf, ifupdown, cloud-init
Description: Fix cloud-init DNS misplacement in ENI config for Proxmox
 Fixes a bug in cloud-init's ENI renderer on Proxmox where the
 dns-nameservers and dns-search directives are placed under the
 loopback interface (lo) instead of the physical interface. This
 causes the system to boot without functional DNS resolution.
 .
 A systemd service runs after cloud-init-local.service and before
 networking.service to correct the generated interfaces file before
 ifupdown brings up the network.

